data.description: This home has been renovated…NEW NEW NEW! The 32X22 Great Room with cathedral ceilings and 2-story windows is absolutely gorgeous! New Pella windows, New roof,  New electrical throughout, New lighting, New cherry hardwood floors, 3 New full baths!  Plus this addition lends extra finished space to the lower level for 1600 sqft ++, making this ideal for a Private Suite including a New wet bar style kitchenette, New full bathroom, and second laundry area. There is a brand New Owners Suite on the upper level built over the 2-car garage with an open loft and 2nd laundry room. Owners Bath highlights include a New freestanding soaking tub, New heated marble floors, New ​​tiled shower and spacious walk-in closet. The 5 and ​a half all newly renovated bathrooms are perfection, ​features include New modern marble floors throughout, New custom ​tiled showers, heated towel rack, New quartz counters and trendy vanities. The home is decked out in beautiful solid Brazilian cherry hardwood floors. The New electric wiring throughout the home has been completely upgraded with rare future-proof 400 amp service , plus New lighting and  Electric Car Charging System and Generator​. Step out to the oversized composite deck and down the New paver steps to the brand New hardscape paver patio, what a perfect place to sit and relax enjoying the mature landscape and privacy. Let’s not forget the New driveway. This colonial home is tucked away at the end of a secluded picturesque cul-de-sac, yet just minutes to all the desired amenities. With all the New improvements this house is ready. Call today to see this beauty in person! ** Accepting backup offers
